eas or specific themes you'd like to explore. Your input is highly valued as we begin planning.\\n\\nThank you,\\n\\nFernan\\n\\nDoes this look good to send?",[],[],{},{},"before you send it can you send to multiple emails?",{},{},"Yes, I can send it to multiple email addresses. Please provide all the email addresses you'd like to include, separated by commas.",[],[],{},{}]
