:"174","To":"175","toolCallId":"176"},{"item":0,"input":0,"sourceOverwrite":"177"},{"id":"178","threadId":"178","labelIds":"179"},{"item":0},{"nodeName":"150","input":"180","type":"181","id":"176","metadata":"182"},"Send a message in Gmail",{"output":"183"},{"item":0},"sendMessage","c817debd-0a45-4f06-881c-6c7817e77884","yes","loadMemoryVariables",["184","185","186","187","188","189"],{},["190","191","192","193","194","195"],{},"saveContext",["196","197","198","199","200","201","202","203"],{"input":"155"},{"output":"204"},{"generations":"205"},{"completionTokens":729,"promptTokens":796,"totalTokens":1525},["206"],{"api_key":"207","model":"208","temperature":0.7},{"generations":"209"},{"completionTokens":68,"promptTokens":1337,"totalTokens":1405},["210"],{"api_key":"211","model":"208","temperature":0.7},"Dear Mr. Frey and Anna,\\n\\nI hope you’re both doing well! I’m excited to share that the preparations for our 2026 Flower Festival, scheduled for May 28, are moving forward nicely. To ensure everything runs smoothly and we capture all the great ideas we’ve discussed, I’d like to arrange a meeting where we can go over the event’s programs and key details.\\n\\n**Proposed meeting:**\\n- **Date:** February 14, 2026\\n- **Time:** 2:00 PM (afternoon)\\n- **Location:** Your office conference room (or a virtual link, if that’s more convenient)\\n\\nDuring our discussion, I suggest we cover the following topics:\\n1. **Overall event concept & theme** – reviewing the vision and any new creative ideas.\\n2. **Program schedule** – finalizing the timeline of performances, workshops, and exhibitions.\\n3. **Vendor selection** – confirming florists, catering, and other service providers.\\n4. **Budget overview** – aligning costs with our projected funding and sponsorships.\\n5. **Marketing & public relations** – outlining promotional tactics, media outreach, and social‑media plans.\\n6. **Volunteer coordination** – recruiting, training, and scheduling volunteers.\\n7. **Logistics & site layout** – layout of stalls, signage, parking, and accessibility.\\n8. **Risk management & safety** – addressing permits, insurance, and contingency plans.\\n9. **Next steps & action items** – assigning responsibilities and setting deadlines.\\n\\nIf the proposed date and time work for you, please let me know, and I’ll send a calendar invitation with a brief agenda. Should you prefer an alternative slot, I’m happy to adjust accordingly.\\n\\nThank you for your continued support and enthusiasm for the Flower Festival. I look forward to collaborating closely to make this event a blooming success!\\n\\nWarm regards,\\n[Your Name]\\n[Your Position]\\n[Your Contact Information]","Planning Meeting for the 2026 Flower Festival","freylee.28@gmail.com, amberbambico.58@gmail.com","fc_fa36ca98-7c64-40e0-a9dc-61ba54144fad",{"previousNode":"111","previousNodeOutput":0,"previousNodeRun":0},"19c23ee8a643b255",["212"],{"Message":"173","Subject":"174","To":"175"},"ai_tool",{"itemIndex":0},"Your email has been sent to freylee.28@gmail.com and amberbambico.58@gmail.com with the subject **“Planning Meeting for the 2026 Flower Festival.”** Let me know if there’s anything else you’d like to adjust or any other email you need help with!",{"lc":1,"type":"213","id":"214","kwargs":"215"},{"lc":1,"type":"213","id":"216","kwargs":"217"},{"lc":1,"type":"213","id":"218","kwargs":"219"},{"lc":1,"type":"213","id":"220","kwargs":"221"},{"lc":1,"type":"213","id":"222","kwargs":"223"},{"lc":1,"type":"213","id":"224","kwargs":"225"},{"lc":1,"type":"213","id":"226","kwargs":"227"},{"lc":1,"type":"213","id":"228","kwargs":"229"},{"lc":1,"type":"213","id":"230","kwargs":"231"},{"lc":1,"type":"213","id":"232","kwargs":"233"},{"lc":1,"type":"213","id":"234","kwargs":"235"},{"lc":1,"type":"213","id":"236","kwargs":"237"},{"lc":1,"type":"213","id":"238","kwargs":"239"},{"lc":1,"type":"213","id":"240","kwargs":"241"},{"lc":1,"type":"213","id":"242","kwargs":"243"},{"lc":1,"type":"213","id":"244","kwa