endar invitation with a brief agenda. Should you prefer an alternative slot, I’m happy to adjust accordingly.\\\\n\\\\nThank you for your continued support and enthusiasm for the Flower Festival. I look forward to collaborating closely to make this event a blooming success!\\\\n\\\\nWarm regards,\\\\n[Your Name]\\\\n[Your Position]\\\\n[Your Contact Information]\\",\\"Subject\\":\\"Planning Meeting for the 2026 Flower Festival\\",\\"To\\":\\"freylee.28@gmail.com, amberbambico.58@gmail.com\\",\\"id\\":\\"fc_fa36ca98-7c64-40e0-a9dc-61ba54144fad\\"}\\nTool: [{\\"id\\":\\"19c23ee8a643b255\\",\\"threadId\\":\\"19c23ee8a643b255\\",\\"labelIds\\":[\\"SENT\\"]}]",{"lc":1,"type":"255","id":"258"},"SENT","constructor",["259","260","261"],{"content":"262","additional_kwargs":"263","response_metadata":"264"},["259","260","265"],{"content":"266","tool_calls":"267","invalid_tool_calls":"268","additional_kwargs":"269","response_metadata":"270"},["259","260","261"],{"content":"271","additional_kwargs":"272","response_metadata":"273"},["259","260","265"],{"content":"274","tool_calls":"275","invalid_tool_calls":"276","additional_kwargs":"277","response_metadata":"278"},["259","260","261"],{"content":"279","additional_kwargs":"280","response_metadata":"281"},["259","260","265"],{"content":"282","tool_calls":"283","invalid_tool_calls":"284","additional_kwargs":"285","response_metadata":"286"},["259","260","261"],{"content":"262","additional_kwargs":"263","response_metadata":"264"},["259","260","265"],{"content":"266","tool_calls":"267","invalid_tool_calls":"268","additional_kwargs":"269","response_metadata":"270"},["259","260","261"],{"content":"271","additional_kwargs":"272","response_metadata":"273"},["259","260","265"],{"content":"274","tool_calls":"275","invalid_tool_calls":"276","additional_kwargs":"277","response_metadata":"278"},["259","260","261"],{"content":"279","additional_kwargs":"280","response_metadata":"281"},["259","260","265"],{"content":"282","tool_calls":"283","inval