 safety** – site layout, permits, crowd management, and contingency plans.  \\n> \\n> If there are any additional topics you’d like to add, please let me know and I’ll make sure they’re on the agenda. I’m looking forward to collaborating with you both to make the Flower Festival a vibrant and successful celebration.\\n> \\n> Thanks for your time, and I’ll await your confirmation of the meeting slot.  \\n> \\n> Best regards,  \\n> [Your Name]  \\n> [Your Position]  \\n> [Your Contact Information]  \\n\\n---\\n\\nFeel free to let me know if you’d like any tweaks or additional details!",{"lc":1,"type":"134","id":"135","kwargs":"136"},{"lc":1,"type":"134","id":"137","kwargs":"138"},{"lc":1,"type":"134","id":"139","kwargs":"140"},{"lc":1,"type":"134","id":"141","kwargs":"142"},{"lc":1,"type":"134","id":"143","kwargs":"144"},{"lc":1,"type":"134","id":"145","kwargs":"146"},{"lc":1,"type":"134","id":"147","kwargs":"148"},{"lc":1,"type":"134","id":"149","kwargs":"150"},{"lc":1,"type":"134","id":"151","kwargs":"152"},{"lc":1,"type":"134","id":"153","kwargs":"154"},{"lc":1,"type":"134","id":"155","kwargs":"156"},{"lc":1,"type":"134","id":"157","kwargs":"158"},{"lc":1,"type":"134","id":"159","kwargs":"160"},{"lc":1,"type":"134","id":"161","kwargs":"162"},{"lc":1,"type":"134","id":"163","kwargs":"164"},{"lc":1,"type":"134","id":"165","kwargs":"166"},{"lc":1,"type":"134","id":"167","kwargs":"168"},{"lc":1,"type":"134","id":"169","kwargs":"170"},{"lc":1,"type":"134","id":"171","kwargs":"172"},{"lc":1,"type":"134","id":"173","kwargs":"174"},{"lc":1,"type":"134","id":"175","kwargs":"176"},{"lc":1,"type":"134","id":"177","kwargs":"178"},["179"],"System: You are an AI Email Assistant. Your role is to help users draft, improve, and send clear, professional emails based on their instructions.\\n\\nGuidelines:\\n\\nMaintain a polite and professional tone unless the user requests otherwise.\\n\\nAsk for missing details such as recipient, subject, or purpose if unclear.\\n\\nImprove gramma