the full email and send it to both freylee.28@gmail.com and amberbambico.58@gmail.com. Let me know!",[],[],{},{},"yes",{},{},"[Used tools: Tool: Send_a_message_in_Gmail, Input: {}, Result: [{\\"id\\":\\"19c23ee8a643b255\\",\\"threadId\\":\\"19c23ee8a643b255\\",\\"labelIds\\":[\\"SENT\\"]}]] Your email has been sent to freylee.28@gmail.com and amberbambico.58@gmail.com with the subject **“Planning Meeting for the 2026 Flower Festival.”** Let me know if there’s anything else you’d like to adjust or any other email you need help with!",[],[],{},{},"can you resend it to amberbambico.54@gmail.com",{},{},"[Used tools: Tool: Send_a_message_in_Gmail, Input: {}, Result: [{\\"id\\":\\"19c23efaf5057d4a\\",\\"threadId\\":\\"19c23efaf5057d4a\\",\\"labelIds\\":[\\"UNREAD\\",\\"SENT\\",\\"INBOX\\"]}]] The email has been resent to **amberbambico.54@gmail.com**. Let me know if there’s anything else you’d like to adjust or any other messages you need help with!",[],[],{},{},{},{},[],[],{},{},{"text":"107","generationInfo":"234"},"GROQ_API_KEY",{"finish_reason":"235"},"stop"]
